description: A handheld camera pans across an indoor food-court / mall corridor while three people walk from left-to-center early in the clip. The camera moves rightward revealing decorative doors, panels and strings of lights; static signage and pillars remain in view as the scene unfolds.
relationships: camera follows / keeps people in frame

small group of people walking through the mall / food court (window shopping or passing through)
static scene of retail/food stalls and decorative elements being revealed by camera movement
